ygData.messageBody:
You don't know Xillith anywhere *near* well enough to make that accusation,
creep. She happens to be one of the highest level Dark Elf Characters on RZ.
You don't get there by killing other Dark Elves for Rusty Daggers...

Malvolin(Teir'Dal Necromancer)--Rallos Zek
Azalin(Still Retired Human Shadowknight)--Veeshan
